
// This file is UTF8 encoded 

// letter groups:
// A   vowel letters and vowel signs
// B   vowel signs and virama ्
// C   consonants
// Y   vowel letters and vowel signs

// conditional rules
// ?2   use diphthong for "ai"
// ?3   use diphthong for "au"


.replace
